Package com.pizzeria.training.models

Class Pizza

java.lang.Object
com.pizzeria.training.models.Pizza
public class Pizza
extends java.lang.Object
Pizza class for use by Pizzeria restaurant Covers details about size, type, toppings, price, as well as a unique identifier in the mongoDB database
